# Simple Natural Language Test

say "Testing original keywords first..."

ask "What's your name?" into player_name

say "Nice to meet you, " + player_name + "!"

choice "Say Hello" or "Say Goodbye"

if answer is "Say Hello" then
    say "Hello, " + player_name + "!"
end

if answer is "Say Goodbye" then
    say "Goodbye, " + player_name + "!"
end

say "Now testing NEW natural keywords:"
speak "The word 'speak' works!"
tell "The word 'tell' works!"
write "The word 'write' works!"
